android.media
接口 JetPlayer.OnJetEventListener

包容类：
JetPlayer
public static interface JetPlayer.OnJetEventListener

Handles the notification when the JET engine generates an event.

方法摘要
 void onJetEvent(JetPlayer player, short segment, byte track, byte channel, byte controller, byte value)
          Callback for when the JET engine generates a new event.
 void onJetNumQueuedSegmentUpdate(JetPlayer player, int nbSegments)
          Callback for when JET's number of queued segments is updated.
 void onJetPauseUpdate(JetPlayer player, int paused)
          Callback for when JET pause state is updated.

          Callback for when JET's currently playing segment's userID is updated.
 

方法详细信息

onJetEvent

void onJetEvent(JetPlayer player,
                short segment,
                byte track,
                byte channel,
                byte controller,
                byte value)
Callback for when the JET engine generates a new event.

参数：
player - the JET player the event is coming from
segment - 8 bit unsigned value
track - 6 bit unsigned value
channel - 4 bit unsigned value
controller - 7 bit unsigned value
value - 7 bit unsigned value

onJetUserIdUpdate

void onJetUserIdUpdate(JetPlayer player,
                       int userId,
                       int repeatCount)
Callback for when JET's currently playing segment's userID is updated.

参数：
player - the JET player the status update is coming from
userId - the ID of the currently playing segment
repeatCount - the repetition count for the segment (0 means it plays once)

onJetNumQueuedSegmentUpdate

void onJetNumQueuedSegmentUpdate(JetPlayer player,
                                 int nbSegments)
Callback for when JET's number of queued segments is updated.

参数：
player - the JET player the status update is coming from
nbSegments - the number of segments in the JET queue

onJetPauseUpdate

void onJetPauseUpdate(JetPlayer player,
                      int paused)
Callback for when JET pause state is updated.

参数：
player - the JET player the status update is coming from
paused - indicates whether JET is paused (1) or not (0)
